[SDG-TERM]: sdgfetch and sdgtip run on every new terminal window
[SDG-TERM]: tipme shows a random SDG-OS tip from any terminal
[SDG-TERM]: eza aliases: ls, la, ll, lt give colorful directory listings
[SDG-TERM]: zoxide lets you cd <partial> to jump to any directory
[SDG-TERM]: find uses fzf with bat preview for fuzzy file search
[SDG-TERM]: plz re-runs the last command with sudo
[SDG-TERM]: Ghostty pane splits with Alt+Arrow keys
[SDG-TERM]: cmdhist searches your command history with fzf
[SDG-TERM]: Ctrl+R reloads the Ghostty config
[SDG-TERM]: microfind opens a fuzzy-selected file in micro editor
[SDG-TERM]: cowtip shows a random tip with cowsay and lolcat
